Author: getoily
Text: I’m in a similar situation, but with my parents. I tell my mom about one goddamn panic attack and now I’m constantly being asked if I’m okay. Everyone in my family (other than me, as I’m working) was supposed to go on a trip to Jersey but now my mom doesn’t trust me being home by myself and is staying home. I understand that they want me to be safe but it’s so fucking humiliating.

Author: beezythegiraffe
Text: Hahahahaha wow we are living the same life. (That was an ironic, sob filled laugh btw). Wanna ditch the SOs and go be miserable together? I heard you can even rent houses that dont come equipped with refridgerators.....
